                    "@type": "Question",
                    "name": "What are Dividend Aristocrats?",
                    "acceptedAnswer": {
                        "@type": "Answer",
                        "text": "A Dividend Aristocrat is a company in the S&amp;amp;P 500 that has paid and increased its base dividend every year for at least 25 consecutive years.",
                        "author": {
                            "@type": "Organization",
